pe=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1e491b2 elementor-widget__width-auto elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"1e491b2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h6 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Minimum Investment: $100,000<\/h6>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-285c1a2 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"285c1a2\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">T\u00fcrkiye Citizenship by Investment Program<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-23a27cd e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"23a27cd\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f16fa7f elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f16fa7f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>\u00a0<\/p><p>The T\u00fcrkiye Citizenship by Investment Program (previously named the Turkey Citizenship by Investment Program) was launched in January 2017 to attract foreign direct investment to and boost growth in the country\u2019s real estate sector. The program allows applicants to choose from a number of different types of economic contributions to Turkish society, thereby developing the country\u2019s economy.<\/p><p>With the city of Istanbul embracing Europe and Asia on the Bosphorus Strait, T\u00fcrkiye is a transcontinental Eurasian country. Its location at the crossroads of Europe and Asia makes it a country of significant geostrategic importance.<\/p><p>There are diverse and multiple investment options available for obtaining citizenship of T\u00fcrkiye, here are some of the available investment options<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-69e943f e-grid e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"69e943f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-585e2b3 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"585e2b3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/calendar.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                        \t\t  \t<p>Processing period of 4 to 6 months<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b8069c3 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"b8069c3\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/02\/bank.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                        \t\t  \t<p>Deposit in a Turkish bank account at least $500,000<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f7e9023 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"f7e9023\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/key.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                        \t\t  \t<p>A minimum investment of US$400,000 in real estate.<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c12b661 ekit-equal-height-disable elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-elementskit-icon-box\" data-id=\"c12b661\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;,&quot;_animation_delay&quot;:1}\" data-widget_type=\"elementskit-icon-box.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"ekit-wid-con\" >        <!-- link opening -->\n                <!-- end link opening -->\n\n        <div class=\"elementskit-infobox text-left text-left icon-top-align elementor-animation-  gradient-active  hover_from_left\">\n                            <div class=\"elementskit-box-header\">\n                <div class=\"elementskit-info-box-icon \">\n                    <img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/03\/taxes-4.png\" class=\"attachment- size-\" alt=\"\" \/>                <\/div>\n          <\/div>\n                <div class=\"box-body\">\n                        \t\t  \t<p>Invest in Turkish real estate or a Venture Capital Investment Fund.<\/p>\n                                <\/div>\n        \n        \n                <\/div>\n        <\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-19c911b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"19c911b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-790de7d e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"790de7d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-921759e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"921759e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Purchase Property<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c9858a4 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"c9858a4\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The first Citizenship by Investment option requires you to invest a minimum US$400,000 real estate purchase. Moreover, you pay 1-8% VAT on a new property, while there is no VAT for resale.<\/p><p>Stamp duty is 4%, divided between you, the buyer, and the seller (although in the resale market, you will bear the cost of the entire 4%). Additionally, you pay 2% of the 4% real estate commission, while the seller covers the remaining 2%.<\/p><p>Furthermore, it\u2019s worth noting that there is no Turkish government contribution amount. Additionally, you won\u2019t need to worry about due diligence fees or administrative fees, except for minor negligible charges.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b20f07d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b20f07d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Make A Bank Deposit<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e803372 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"e803372\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Deposit in a Turkish bank account at least $500,000 or other foreign currency\u2019s worth of Turkish lira.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a08c37f elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"a08c37f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Contribute to an Approved Public Benefit Project<\/h2>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6fbaa04 elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"6fbaa04\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;xpro-anim-mask-from-left&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>The Presidency of the Republic of T\u00fcrkiye Investment Option sets out the conditions. These are by \u201cbuying real estate investment fund shares or venture capital investment fund shares worth a minimum of USD 500,000 or equivalent foreign currency with the condition that they are not sold for at least three years, as attested by the Capital Markets Board of T\u00fcrkiye\u201d.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cee4440 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"cee4440\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c999b8d elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"c999b8d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/daacb94022.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-8303\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/daacb94022.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/daacb94022-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/forecastmigration.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/09\/daacb94022-768x511.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-da5842a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"da5842a\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a7e803e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-child\" data-id=\"a7e803e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_backgroun